Comment: 10,0:09:20.93,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if I did, I couldn't ride it.
Comment: 10,0:09:23.25,0:09:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, I don't want to be late.
Comment: 10,0:09:31.69,0:09:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a ride?
Comment: 10,0:09:33.64,0:09:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never flown double before, but I might be able to pull it off.
Comment: 10,0:09:37.14,0:09:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Thank you!
Comment: 10,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are nice witches too!
Comment: 10,0:09:41.37,0:09:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kagari Atsuko! Call me Akko!
Comment: 10,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm Lotte.
Comment: 10,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quick, we're running out of time.
Comment: 10,0:09:47.78,0:09:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 10,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take off.
Comment: 10,0:09:52.97,0:09:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly, my broom.
Comment: 10,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tia Freyre!
Comment: 10,0:10:01.88,0:10:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, no way!
Comment: 10,0:10:03.05,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're flying! We're flying! We're flying! We're fly—
Comment: 10,0:10:07.61,0:10:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think our luggage is too heavy.
Comment: 10,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Open, gateway to Luna Nova!
Comment: 10,0:10:15.39,0:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? What is this? What is this? What is this?!
Comment: 10,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do this! Get me off this thing!
Comment: 10,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Settle down a bit!
Comment: 10,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My stuff!
Comment: 10,0:10:35.87,0:10:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Normal witches are unable to enter the legendary forest of Arcturus."
Comment: 10,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This has never happened before. Something's off!
Comment: 10,0:10:52.01,0:10:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell me you're carrying salt.
Comment: 10,0:10:54.57,0:10:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Salt?
Comment: 10,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Leylines hate salt!
Comment: 10,0:11:01.75,0:11:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's this?
Comment: 10,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Comment: 10,0:11:04.44,0:11:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pickled plums.
Comment: 10,0:11:05.69,0:11:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Toss it!
Comment: 10,0:11:06.40,0:11:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't survive without pickled plum—
Comment: 10,0:11:10.21,0:11:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, throw it away!
Comment: 10,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Fine!
Comment: 10,0:11:16.66,0:11:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My treasure!
Comment: 10,0:11:18.22,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, it's dangerous!
Comment: 10,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Comment: 10,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Alcor?
Comment: 10,0:12:00.21,0:12:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be—Arcturus Forest?!{## i wonder how many people will think this is wrong/inconsistent}
Comment: 10,0:12:22.51,0:12:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! My treasure is safe!
Comment: 10,0:12:29.44,0:12:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She's dead!
Comment: 10,0:12:32.04,0:12:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the very definition of trouble.
Comment: 10,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're alive!
Comment: 10,0:12:36.46,0:12:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that won't kill a witch.
Comment: 10,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte!
Comment: 10,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Did you get hurt?
Comment: 10,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, but my broom isn't.
Comment: 10,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears we reached my destination.
Comment: 10,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Destination?
Comment: 10,0:12:54.03,0:12:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this is Luna Nova?
Comment: 10,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the ceremony?
Comment: 10,0:12:57.30,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the place. I've never seen this forest before.
Comment: 10,0:13:08.58,0:13:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Arcturus Forest.
Comment: 10,0:13:11.31,0:13:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Arcturus?
Comment: 10,0:13:13.13,0:13:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! The forbidden forest?!
Comment: 10,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Comment: 10,0:13:16.63,0:13:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a forest of ancient legend.\NThis is sacred land, protected by the magic tree.{## i'm sure there are more forests of ancient legend}{batch fix}
Comment: 10,0:13:21.61,0:13:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that even witches can hardly escape once they've wandered in.
Comment: 10,0:13:25.36,0:13:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What, that's no good! How am I supposed to make matriculation now?
Comment: 10,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You should worry more about being stuck here your entire life.
Comment: 10,0:13:32.46,0:13:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't scare me like that!
Comment: 10,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Found some of my stuff!
Comment: 10,0:13:41.16,0:13:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Comment: 10,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko, get back!
Comment: 10,0:13:54.46,0:13:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Comment: 10,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that thing?!
Comment: 10,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mandrake, a man-eating plant. {the CCs say "maneating" for this line}{## sucy disagrees}{batch?}
Comment: 10,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Comment: 10,0:14:19.76,0:14:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Comment: 10,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Comment: 10,0:14:23.11,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Comment: 10,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here for a sec.
Comment: 10,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Comment: 10,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand in here.
Comment: 10,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Juras Haras Haras.
Comment: 10,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Comment: 10,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Cast the spell.
Comment: 10,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Spell?
Comment: 10,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will that help us get out?
Comment: 10,0:14:44.36,0:14:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kutchur Katela Flala.
Comment: 10,0:14:46.63,0:14:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kutchur Kat... F-Fla-fla?
Comment: 10,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kutchur Katela {\i1}Flala{\i0}.
Comment: 10,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shout it from your belly!
Comment: 10,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kutchur Katela Flala!
Comment: 10,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&\fad(0,1000)}Flala!
Comment: 10,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H60&\fad(0,1000)}Flala!
Comment: 10,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H80&\fad(0,1483)}Flala!
Comment: 10,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Comment: 10,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya.
Comment: 10,0:15:24.57,0:15:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this thing? What did that spell just do?
Comment: 10,0:15:26.82,0:15:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You said "Hey stupid, come eat me\Nif you want to shut me up."
Comment: 10,0:15:30.49,0:15:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 10,0:15:31.28,0:15:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a mythical cockatrice which lives only in Arcturus Forest.
Comment: 10,0:15:36.06,0:15:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They say its feathers contain a deadly poison.
Comment: 10,0:15:38.23,0:15:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A collector of deadly poisons can't ignore such a super rare item.{she doesn't actually say 'like her' so this fits and is right}
Comment: 10,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Distract it for me.
Comment: 10,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll grab a feather in the meantime.
Comment: 10,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you saying you used us as bait?!
Comment: 10,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, you're a sacrifice.
Comment: 10,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shout that line one more time!
Comment: 10,0:15:51.86,0:15:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck no!
Comment: 10,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, keep on dodging.
Comment: 10,0:16:00.04,0:16:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be petrified if you get caught in its breath.
Comment: 10,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Petrified?
Comment: 10,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Comment: 10,0:16:18.23,0:16:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mine.
Comment: 10,0:16:27.92,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-We can't stop!
Comment: 10,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Comment: 10,0:16:42.00,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 10,0:16:42.89,0:16:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get out of here.
Comment: 10,0:16:45.85,0:16:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we'll make it\Nif we keep on wasting time!
Comment: 10,0:16:48.93,0:16:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Comment: 10,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My leg...
Comment: 10,0:16:52.28,0:16:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over, we can't get there in time...{## repetition}
Comment: 10,0:16:55.36,0:16:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Comment: 10,0:16:58.06,0:17:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never give up!
Comment: 10,0:17:03.13,0:17:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go...
Comment: 10,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a witch!
Comment: 10,0:17:09.57,0:17:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If I reach out...{## her story etc}
Comment: 10,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sure to begin!
Comment: 10,0:17:14.84,0:17:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thrilling...
Comment: 10,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And exciting...
Comment: 10,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My very own story!
Comment: 10,0:17:31.11,0:17:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... Chariot's magic staff!
Comment: 10,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, wait here and hide.
Comment: 10,0:17:48.57,0:17:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:17:54.88,0:17:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kutchur Katela Flala!
Comment: 10,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Comment: 10,0:17:59.14,0:18:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Birdbrain, here I am!\NTry to catch me if you can! {this is a line used in kind of literature and/or the game tag, it can't exactly be translated straight}{## made it rhyme}
Comment: 10,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it worked.
Comment: 10,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Comment: 10,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop on.
Comment: 10,0:18:45.40,0:18:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, um...
Comment: 10,0:18:49.19,0:18:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sucy. Sucy Manbavaran.
Comment: 10,0:18:52.77,0:18:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sucy.
Comment: 10,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know when to give up!
Comment: 10,0:19:04.78,0:19:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't all get away on one broom!
Comment: 10,0:19:10.54,0:19:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Comment: 10,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he's breathing fire!
Comment: 10,0:19:18.39,0:19:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing in such a place?
Comment: 10,0:19:21.60,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, we're burning!
Comment: 10,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Comment: 10,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shiny Rod!
Comment: 10,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot hot hot hot hot!
Comment: 10,0:19:37.64,0:19:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Words!
Comment: 10,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Cast the spell!
Comment: 10,0:19:46.38,0:19:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff!
Comment: 10,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Noctu Orfei!
Comment: 10,0:19:49.33,0:19:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Noctu... Orfei!{## yeah this doesn't like orfei at all}{they pronounce it differently every time, it's fine}
Comment: 10,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Aude!
Comment: 10,0:19:54.44,0:19:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aude!
Comment: 10,0:19:56.51,0:19:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraetor!
Comment: 10,0:19:59.92,0:20:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiny Arc!
Comment: 10,0:20:49.52,0:20:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, did you have an enjoyable vacation?
Comment: 10,0:20:53.92,0:20:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Our academy has raised countless great witches in its long history.
Comment: 10,0:20:58.73,0:21:04.07,Default,,15,15,0,,By crossing its threshold once more, you pledge yourself\Nto act with pride, decorum, and a sense of modesty.{## sorry but it's just too long} {BD}
Comment: 10,0:21:04.42,0:21:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Devote yourselves to the study of magic.
Comment: 10,0:21:08.75,0:21:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we shall commence the matriculation cere—
Comment: 10,0:21:32.66,0:21:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Comment: 10,0:21:35.30,0:21:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it!
Comment: 10,0:21:38.11,0:21:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Comment: 10,0:21:43.88,0:21:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My word, that was an unprecedented ceremony.
Comment: 10,0:21:47.51,0:21:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It is only due to the headmaster's special permission
Comment: 10,0:21:50.87,0:21:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have been allowed to enroll.
Comment: 10,0:21:52.99,0:21:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Make certain not to forget your debt.
Comment: 10,0:21:55.26,0:21:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 10,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Greet your roommates.
Comment: 10,0:22:03.99,0:22:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For the next three years, you three can expect particularly strict instruction.
Comment: 10,0:22:13.68,0:22:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kagari Atsuko. Let's be friends!
